  "prompt": "Should I take mass gainer or whey protein?",
  "response": "The choice between mass gainer and whey protein depends on your specific fitness goals:\n\nWhey Protein:\n- Better for muscle recovery and building lean muscle\n- Lower in calories\n- Higher protein concentration\n- Good for people wanting to add muscle while maintaining low body fat\n- Ideal for athletes and those doing strength training\n\nMass Gainer:\n- Higher in calories and carbohydrates\n- Helps people who struggle to gain weight\n- Good for those trying to bulk up and increase overall body mass\n- Contains more nutrients and calories\n- Suitable for people with fast metabolisms or who are underweight\n\nRecommended choice:\n- If you want to build muscle and lose fat: Whey protein\n- If you want to gain weight and increase muscle mass: Mass gainer\n- If you have difficulty eating enough calories: Mass gainer\n\nConsider consulting a nutritionist or fitness professional for personalized advice based on your individual body type, metabolism, and fitness goals.",
